OL,3,CResidents 'forgotten' following Post
OL,4,COffice closure weeks after bank closes
OL,6,FResidents in Moffat fear they are
OL,7,Fbeing 'forgotten' after the town's
OL,8,FPost Office closed without warning.
OL,10,FThe post office counter, located
OL,11,Finside a local petrol station,
OL,12,Ftemporarily closed on 26 February
OL,13,Fleaving the community without any
OL,14,Fregular in-person banking and postal
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FIt comes after the town's last
OL,18,Fremaining bank closed its doors in
OL,19,FNovember.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
