OL,3,CResidents 'forgotten' following Post
OL,4,COffice closure weeks after bank closes
OL,6,FCampaigner Evelyn Atkins, who fought
OL,7,Fto keep the bank open, described the
OL,8,Fsituation as "devastating."
OL,10,FShe said: "It's totally inconvenient
OL,11,Fnot to have any services within a town
OL,12,Fthis size.
OL,14,F"It's a busy, tourist town. When the
OL,15,Fcaravan site opens up and they won't
OL,16,Fhave the availability to get cash.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
