OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773846665
OL,3,CResidents 'forgotten' following Post
OL,4,COffice closure weeks after bank closes
OL,6,F"Pensioners - where do they get their
OL,7,Fpension from? If they don't get it
OL,8,Fdirect to their bank account, they've
OL,9,Fgot to travel to Lockerbie. It's a sad
OL,10,Fstate of affairs, really."
OL,12,FBusinesses and residents that rely on
OL,13,Fcash are now forced to make a round
OL,14,Ftrip of more than 40 miles to Dumfries
OL,15,Fto deposit money.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
