PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773846665
OL,3,CResidents 'forgotten' following Post
OL,4,COffice closure weeks after bank closes
OL,6,FClaire Jenkins, owner of The Laundry
OL,7,FRoom, said: "We have to go all the way
OL,8,Fto Dumfries. We need to bag our money,
OL,9,Fbank our money and then come all the
OL,10,Fway back again. That's like an hour
OL,11,Fand a half out of our day, out of a
OL,12,Fbusy day when we're all not got enough
OL,13,Fhours in the day for our work.
OL,15,F"It is affecting everybody. To not
OL,16,Fhave a bank and the post office is
OL,17,Fhuge."
OL,19,FFiona Young, manager of Manse
OL,20,FInteriors & Bistro, said it doesn't
OL,21,Ffeel safe travelling with so much cash.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
