OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773846665
OL,3,CResidents 'forgotten' following Post
OL,4,COffice closure weeks after bank closes
OL,6,F"We had the bank across the road so
OL,7,Ffrom a safety point of view, it was
OL,8,Fjust there," she said.
OL,10,F"Rather than 22 miles away, the safety
OL,11,Fof carrying the money, is a big issue
OL,12,Fnow as well.
OL,14,F"And not knowing when and not knowing
OL,15,Fwhen or if at all it'll open again.
OL,16,FThat's a big question."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
