OL,3,CResidents 'forgotten' following Post
OL,4,COffice closure weeks after bank closes
OL,6,FA Post Office spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Moffat Post Office has temporarily
OL,8,Fclosed with immediate effect on 27
OL,9,FFebruary due to unexpected operational
OL,10,Freasons beyond our control.
OL,12,F"We know how important Post Office
OL,13,Fservices including banking are to this
OL,14,Fcommunity and we are working hard to
OL,15,Frestore service to the community as
OL,16,Fsoon as possible."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
