PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773846665
OL,3,CResidents 'forgotten' following Post
OL,4,COffice closure weeks after bank closes
OL,6,FMSP Craig Hoy has previously describe
OL,7,Fthe bank's closure as "deeply
OL,8,Fconcerning" and held a debate in
OL,9,FHolyrood to discuss the spate of
OL,10,Fclosures in the south of Scotland.
OL,12,FFollowing the Post Office closure, he
OL,13,Ftold ITV Border: "What we're seeing
OL,14,Fbecause of the temporary closure of
OL,15,Fthe Post Office is that Moffat could
OL,16,Fbe left without cash at certain
OL,17,Fpoints, and that will be a real
OL,18,Fconcern for residents and a real
OL,19,Fconcern for businesses."
